Our Show > #1418: The Ungrateful Passenger


#1418: The Ungrateful Passenger

The driver's revenge.


 



Description: 



This week on Car Talk, 



Jere agreed to drive her sister's co-worker's husband to work.
          How did he thank her? By telling everyone (including Jere) 
              she's a stinko driver. 

Elsewhere, Dorothy had to rig a wire to her Land Rover's fan to keep it
         from shredding the radiator, during her daily drive in Botswana.
            Will this brilliant solution cook her engine? 

Also, on Stump the Chumps, we find out if the "Godfather strategy"
       helped Joe convince his brother-in-law to remove an old Honda Civic
          from Joe's yard; 

and did a hammer and a "Hey guys, watch this!" really fix Hendie's brake noise?



               All this and more, this week no car Talk.
